{"version": 2, "width": 100, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1764950700, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "HELIX plan: authority-ranked gaps, ready for the next mode"}
[0.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# Brief and PRD are aligned. Run /helix align for an authority-ranked gap list \u2014 each one handing off cleanly to the next workflow mode.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m> Use /helix align on this project and produce an authority-ranked plan. For each non-aligned gap, name the destination artifact type, the deliverable shape, the suggested next workflow mode, and evidence references.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.0, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Skill(skill='helix', args='align')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.5, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 Launching skill: helix\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.8, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Bash(command=\"find docs/helix -type f -name '*.md'\", description='Inventory authority artifacts')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.3, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 4 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.6, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/00-discover/product-vision.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.1, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 20 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.4, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.9, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 42 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.2, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/01-frame/features/FEAT-001-csv-ingest.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.7, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 33 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.0, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/01-frame/concerns.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.5, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 24 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.8, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# Every finding carries four fields \u2014 destination, deliverable, next mode, evidence \u2014 so the next agent can pick it up without re-reading the whole tree.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
